text: Toronto Blue Jays vs. Kansas City Royals live score updates Game 2 ALCS Toronto vs. Kansas City game 2 live score updates Kansas City Royals staring pitcher Yordano Ventura, left, celebrates with shortstop Alcides Escobar after Escobar made a diving catch to turn a double play against the Toronto Blue Jays during the second inning in Game 2 of baseball's American League Championship Series, Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Kansas City, Mo.
